_sText:
In this map if you break the underground middle glass you'll get a surprise and unlock the red and yellow buttons, they both activate or de-activate lights. The main one, the red, only does it once, and controls the begginig white lights, to activate the lights again you'll have to find how...

 The secondary one, the yellow, activates the red lights in the underground room, that at the beggining are blackedout, this one can be use infinite times...

Its a closed map, and it has varius tunnels, and it doesen't have a buy zone, but numerous weapons, some hidden, scatterd all around.

All the light are basic (because i want to)

Has 3 rooms...enjoy.., free to comment good or bad...use it has you like, but tell me first...
